From 495efcc29daf0e0575358040c6c3bd80e3988c03 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: johnnylibretexts <johnny@johnnyrobot.ai>
Date: Thu, 9 Jul 2026 19:26:03 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 12/16] feat(pronunciation): login-free practice embed
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- PronunciationQuestion.vue mode="practice": posts the recording straight to
  the jingo scorer /practice-score and renders feedback only — no ADAPT upload,
  no gradebook. questionId/problemJwt/audioUploadUrl are now optional (unused in
  practice).
- New anonymous page /embed/pronunciation (layout "blank", no auth middleware)
  that mounts only the recorder in practice mode; reads env URLs from
  window.config and exercise_id/lang/prompt from the query string.
- Pairs with the jingo scorer /practice-score endpoint and the mirror
  [[pron|id|lang|prompt]] -> <iframe allow="microphone"> injection.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_01CRePd9rbvtz6UqFuuYMi9U
(cherry picked from commit 33dc2f8040b4e1444dc47e9c48cfd32d49c8b9ac)
